text.tspan: Toward automated identification of semantically compatible words
Randomly matched ~ 300 seed words into 18K pairs
How much do you agree with that <word1> and <word2>
can refer to the same thing, animal or person?

flowRoot.flowPara: In a reasonably normal state of affairs!
Linguistic expressions w1 and w2 are compatible, iff in a reasonably normal state of affairs, they can both thruthfully refer to the same thing. If they cannot, then they are incompatible.
